{"tid":2515241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國研究發現，輝瑞疫苗對新冠變異病毒並無「全面防護」","createTime":"2021-05-03T23:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T02:13:19.000Z","uid":294518,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"593f76cbca7a28082615dbb797988501b71fafc8","tid":2515241,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:45:10.000Z","msg":"UK Study Finds Pfizer Vaccine Doesn't Offer &quot;Full Protection&quot; From Mutant COVID Strains<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.zerohedge.com/covid-19/uk-study-finds-pfizer-vaccine-doesnt-offer-full-protection-mutant-covid-strains\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zerohedge.com%2Fcovid-19%2Fuk-study-finds-pfizer-vaccine-doesnt-offer-full-protection-mutant-covid-strains&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnmhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=6cc2f1b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zerohedge.com/covid-19/uk-study-finds-pfizer-vaccine-doesnt-offer-full-protection-mutant-covid-strains</a><br />\n英國研究發現，輝瑞疫苗對新冠變異病毒並無「全面防護」"},{"pid":"6072eec92fc4457c4146b036a01769e6040e1f7a","tid":2515241,"uid":81214,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:46:25.000Z","msg":"人地研發時候都冇諗過會變種"},{"pid":"9953005037b188bc154dcfd1f3e5b335c58ac657","tid":2515241,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:46:55.000Z","msg":"這項研究由倫敦帝國理工學院於週五下午發表在《科學》雜誌上，主要研究了醫護人員在注射了第一針輝瑞疫苗後的免疫反應。<br />\n<br />\n經研究發現，曾感染過新冠病毒的人,通常對變種病毒的防禦能力明顯增強。那些只接種過疫苗但未曾被感染的人，表現出的免疫反應則是「在第一針接種以後免疫反應不太強烈，這可能使他們面臨感染變異病株的風險。」 研究結果顯示，那些接種過輝瑞公司疫苗的人,並不能完全免於變異病株的感染。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，週五發佈的另一項研究也得出了類似的結論。另一項研究也顯示出,一些已經接種了第一針疫苗的人,仍然因為出現了新冠症狀而進入了醫院治療。<br />\n<br />\n據週五公佈的最新數據，65%的英國成年人已經接受了至少一劑疫苗，有3,736,654人在過去7天內接種了疫苗。同時，該國超過了25%的成年人已經接種了兩劑疫苗。英國現在已經接種了8,748,962劑COVID-19疫苗，而美國剛剛宣佈，1億美國人現在已經完全接種了疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n但現有的最新研究數據表明，只打過一針疫苗的人仍然很脆弱。儘管研究人員表明，沒有疫苗是100%完美的，免疫失敗的情況也是可以想象的。但也有人認為，最脆弱的（最可能感染病毒的）人可能會在接種了一次疫苗後就過早的放鬆了警惕。<br />\n<br />\n這項研究分析了12月初至4月初期間英格蘭、蘇格蘭和威爾士所有醫院約總數四分之一的病人，這是最早研究接種疫苗影響隨後入院人數的研究之一。<br />\n<br />\n來自利物浦大學的研究負責人卡魯姆&middot;辛普爾（Calum Semple）教授告訴BBC，這些數據 代表了少數疫苗失敗真實的有力證據。"},{"pid":"363c34f6674f8fe601048d6de9e21c239bf2240e","tid":2515241,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:47:57.000Z","msg":"所以要研發第二代mRNA疫苗，不過科興國藥嗰啲對變種病毒仲有效咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e284f8bfada3ed84a18b0b9f03ce60a7fcddd9eb","tid":2515241,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:48:33.000Z","msg":"英國研究"},{"pid":"f14620be1c1d08059a0c5f8adc16bbce558f87a7","tid":2515241,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:50:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.imperial.ac.uk/news/220613/prior-sarscov2-infection-boosts-response-variants/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imperial.ac.uk%2Fnews%2F220613%2Fprior-sarscov2-infection-boosts-response-variants%2F&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnmhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=f15ef871\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.imperial.ac.uk/news/220613/prior-sarscov2-infection-boosts-response-variants/</a><br />\nPrior SARS-CoV-2 infection boosts response to variants after first vaccine dose<br />\n原文<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbVDRvAwbvVPEFSQNrRvZLKV4rHxf9P4E6bFWcH3iCmwC?filename=voCuqjC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvoCuqjC.png&h=ac51f07d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"becc220460dd93379b75daa602874c22ef845e98","tid":2515241,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRtERXkJCtBNxv2cskUcFDNbHVUVyRQeKqNutg2v48Rsm?filename=JdajNx7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJdajNx7.png&h=306bc305&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe2eebe851627331edf265d533846e44485fb31e","tid":2515241,"uid":117584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":